WEBVTT

00:04.125 --> 00:06.834
Here's pluto's bowl.
And his leash.

00:06.834 --> 00:10.166
And a big bag of pluto's favorite treats.

00:10.166 --> 00:12.041
He only gets a treat when he's good.

00:12.041 --> 00:14.542
Why that's all the time, isn't it, pluto?

00:14.792 --> 00:17.375
Whoa! Easy with those
treats, minnie.

00:17.375 --> 00:18.959
They're very fattening.

00:19.208 --> 00:21.125
Okay, boy, I'll see you in a month.

00:21.125 --> 00:23.667
My little pluto. My little
buddy wuddy wo wo!

00:25.166 --> 00:27.083
My little minnie, my little wo wo!

00:28.208 --> 00:30.208
Take good care of my pluto!

00:30.709 --> 00:32.959
We're going to have so much fun!

00:34.667 --> 00:37.291
Oh, I know I shouldn't,
but I can't help myself!

00:41.000 --> 00:43.166
Oh, hi Mickey.
Pluto's fine.

00:43.166 --> 00:45.667
No, I didn't give him all those treats.

00:45.667 --> 00:48.583
<i>Oh good. Remember,
those treats are very fattening.</i>

00:52.041 --> 00:54.333
<i>Oh, minnie.
I miss pluto so much,</i>

00:54.583 --> 00:56.375
<i>I wish I could see him now.</i>

00:56.959 --> 01:00.000
<i>That's it. I'm coming home
early. I'll be over later today.</i>

01:00.500 --> 01:03.083
Don't worry, pluto!
I'll get you back into shape.

01:04.583 --> 01:07.125
A nice slimming sweater is what you need.

01:08.375 --> 01:10.625
Perfect! Mickey will
never know the difference.

01:20.583 --> 01:22.875
A sauna will melt away those lbs.

01:22.875 --> 01:25.208
After all, it worked for me.

01:27.834 --> 01:28.834
Oh!

01:37.458 --> 01:38.458
Phew.

01:40.041 --> 01:42.125
I'm going to see my pluto,
my pluto, my pluto.

01:43.208 --> 01:45.792
Come on, pluto!
Let's go for a jog.

01:46.041 --> 01:47.041
Nah.

01:47.333 --> 01:50.000
Oh, Mickey's going to be so disappointed.

01:52.667 --> 01:55.041
That's it! Pluto just
needs some motivation.

01:55.500 --> 01:57.166
Yoo-hoo.
Pluto.

01:57.834 --> 01:59.417
Special delivery.

01:59.792 --> 02:00.792
Huh?

02:18.291 --> 02:19.500
Perfect!

02:24.250 --> 02:27.208
Oh, pluto! It's working! We did it.

02:29.000 --> 02:30.208
Whoa!

02:31.542 --> 02:32.625
Oh, dear.

02:32.625 --> 02:34.125
Oh! Oh!

02:34.125 --> 02:35.875
Whoa!

02:37.000 --> 02:38.458
Pluto!

02:58.208 --> 03:00.041
Oh, pluto!

03:00.041 --> 03:01.166
Ahhh!

03:04.709 --> 03:06.166
Pluto! Help!

03:20.083 --> 03:22.500
Pluto, you're ripped!

03:22.500 --> 03:24.291
Wow, minnie, he looks great!

03:24.291 --> 03:27.542
I was pretty sure I was going to
come home to find a big, fat pluto.
